These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, tea, 7up
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, parkour, badminton
1. the person who's sport is parkour is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person drinking water is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | water | tea | 7up   |
| Sport      | golf    | parkour  | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, hot-chocolate, milk
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, thai, indian
1. the brazilian is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the thai is on the far left##1
3. the thai is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite     | milk      |
| Nationality   | thai | brazilian | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, coffee
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, spinach, lettuce
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | coffee  | lemonade       |
| Food       | kiwi     | spinach | lettuce |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, cauliflower, pepper
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, filmmaking, skydiving
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | pepper    | cauliflower     | lettuce |
| Hobby   | skydiving | drawing | filmmaking     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: horse, dog, mouse
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, train, subway
1. the person driving the train is the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | dog | horse     | mouse |
| Transport   | subway        | bus | train    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: potato, corn, pineapple
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, jet-ski, tram
1. the person eating potato is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person eating corn is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person eating pineapple is the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | pineapple | potato      | corn  |
| Transport   | skateboard       | jet-ski | tram |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, pop, gospel
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, dog, rabbit
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of pop is the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel      | metal     | pop    |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | rabbit | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
