2. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person eating apricot is the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | nectarine | papaya | apricot      |
| Hobby   | video-games     | dancing | chess |

