.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, sudoku, collecting
3 different pets are kept: goat, cat, ferret
1. the owner of the goat is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | collecting | sudoku | baking  |
| Pet     | ferret     | goat      | cat |

