.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, mirinda
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, satire, spy
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | 7up   | hot-chocolate    | mirinda    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | drama | spy |

