1. the fan of indie is in the middle##1
2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the italian##1
3. the turkish is on the left of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | indie     | hip-hop   |
| Nationality   | turkish | italian | pakistani |

