.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, lettuce, plum
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, software-developer, librarian
1. the software-developer is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
2. the person eating plum is in the middle##1
3. the security-guard is on the right of the person eating plum##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | carrot     | plum   | lettuce     |
| Job    | librarian | software-developer | security-guard |

