.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-14::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, musician, software-developer
3 different pets are kept: frog, rabbit, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the software-developer##1
2. the software-developer is on the left of the musician##1
3. the musician is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Job   | chef    | software-developer | musician |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | frog     | rabbit        |

