.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, water, sprite
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, blues, dubstep
1. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | lemonade  | sprite | water  |
| Music-Genre   | blues | dubstep   | jazz |

