2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the 7upcher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | water | 7up    |
| Job        | photographer    | 7upcher | accountant |

