.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-17::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, engineer, musician
There are 3 different nationalities: french, german, pakistani
1. the pakistani is on the far left##1
2. the software-developer is on the far right##1
3. the french is the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Job           | engineer | musician | software-developer |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | french      | german |

