.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, eggplant, grapes
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, handball
1. the person who's sport is basketball is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | grapes | blueberry       | eggplant  |
| Sport   | handball  | basketball | badminton |

 